<p>100. The Special Rapporteur commends the Government for the measures taken to ensure 
a conducive working environment for human rights defenders in Cyprus. In this connection, 
she would like to reiterate the need to ensure that the right to freedom of assembly is 
respected, in accordance with article 5, point a), of the Declaration on Human Rights 
Defenders. 
